<item>
            <title>[LS-84] Epic 7: Guide &#8212; Audio Generation</title>
                <link>https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-84</link>
                <project id="10099" key="LS">Laxy Studio</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Goal:&lt;/b&gt; Create Stage 3: Audio Generation in the Laxy Studio guide production pipeline. This epic takes fully translated and validated text from the previous pipeline stage and generates production-ready audio.\n\n*Core Requirements:&lt;b&gt;\n&lt;/b&gt; &lt;b&gt;Pipeline Continuation:&lt;/b&gt; Only items &quot;Approved&quot; in Gate 2 (Translation Validation) advance to Audio Generation.\n* &lt;b&gt;Audio QA &amp;amp; Review:&lt;/b&gt; Supply Approval Gate 3, a human-in-the-loop checkpoint for creators to QA the audio.\n* &lt;b&gt;Isolated Regeneration:&lt;/b&gt; Support &quot;Item-Level Re-Entry Logic&quot; to reject/regenerate the audio for specific single items without restarting the entire pipeline.\n\n*Status Update:* 7.1 and 7.2 tickets have been initialized. Remaining tickets for audio generation to follow.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
